data.description: Remodeled inside and out this home is turn key and waiting for your moving truck. New exterior roof, siding and windows provide that curb appeal you have been searching for. Large lot with in ground pool with new heater and pump and cover. Interiors first impression includes super clean look including new kitchen with open floor plan including clean recessed lighting and breakfast bar. Updated tiled bathroom on the upper level with 3 bedrooms. Downstairs offers multi generational living with a tiled shower stall, large bedroom with walk in in closet and another living room or den are or could be 5th bedroom. Beautiful bathroom offers glass door shower with bench and custom tile work . There is a large laundry room with kitchenette sink and refrigerator as well.
